Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:17.96,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,Skies,where the blue birds fly
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:24.19,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,Clouds where the people place their souls on to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:30.18,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,Brighter,the sunshines that go through my tears
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:35.67,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,like searching for what heals my sorrows
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:53.22,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,Cry,when the twilight's come
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:59.23,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,Rise,when the people's prayer's melt in to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:04.69,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,one,to where we'd been together in the sphere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:10.20,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,I'm searching for where you are,my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:16.93,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to put my heart belongs to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:22.86,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to love someone expect for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:29.35,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,That is all my world to been had you in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:34.60,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,I'll call you all the time
